</span>

</td></tr></table>
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td>
<span style="color:rgb(0, 0, 0);font-family:helvetica;font-size:12pt">
Astrophysical foregrounds, in the form of galactic synchrotron, thermal dust, and compact radio sources, contaminate our measurements of the primordial CMB. We use multifrequency observations and target regions of the sky low in foreground power. 
<p>
<p>
</td>
